<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact - Note_Nest</title>
</head>
<style>
    body {
        background-color: #1a1a1a;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .header {
        height: 60px;
        width: 95%;
        margin: 20px auto;
        border: 2px solid #333;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: linear-gradient(200deg, rgb(12, 12, 82), rgb(7, 123, 123));
    }

    .left {
        font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
        margin-top: 18px;
        margin-left: 25px;
        font-size: 26px;
        color: #4a9eff;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .right ul {
        display: flex;
        gap: 35px;
        list-style-type: none;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-right: 25px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #ddd;
    }

    .right ul li {
        cursor: pointer;
        padding: 5px 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .right ul li:hover {
        background-color: #3a3a3a;
        color: #4a9eff;
    }

    .right ul a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
    }

    .contact {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 450px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .card {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #3a3a3a;
        border: 5px solid rgb(59, 59, 126);
        border-radius: 25px;
        padding: 20px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .card h2, .card h3 {
        color: beige;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .card p {
        color: #4a9eff;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .form-card {
        background-color: #2d3a4a;
        border: 5px solid rgb(50, 70, 90);
    }

    .form-card h3 {
        color: beige;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .form-group {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .form-group label {
        display: block;
        color: #4a9eff;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        border: 2px solid rgb(59, 59, 126);
        background-color: #2a2a2a;
        color: white;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .form-group textarea {
        resize: vertical;
        min-height: 100px;
    }

    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus {
        outline: none;
        border-color: #4a9eff;
    }

    .submit-btn {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 12px;
        background-color: rgb(59, 59, 126);
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 16px;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .submit-btn:hover {
        background-color: rgb(80, 80, 150);
    }

    .info-card {
        background-color: #2d4a2d;
        border: 5px solid rgb(40, 70, 40);
    }

    .info-card h3 {
        color: beige;
    }

    .info-card p {
        color: #90ee90;
        text-align: left;
        padding-left: 10px;
    }

    .social-card {
        background-color: #4a4a2d;
        border: 5px solid rgb(80, 80, 50);
    }

    .social-card h3 {
        color: beige;
    }

    .social-card p {
        color: #f0e68c;
    }

    .social-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 20px;
        margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .social-links a {
        color: #4a9eff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 18px;
        padding: 10px 15px;
        background-color: #3a3a3a;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .social-links a:hover {
        background-color: rgb(59, 59, 126);
        color: white;
    }

    @media (max-width: 400px) {
        .header {
            width: 95%;
            flex-direction: row;
            height: 50px;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .left {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        .right ul {
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .contact {
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .social-links {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
        }
    }
</style>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="left">Note_Nest</div>
        <div class="right">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">HOME</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">ABOUT</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">CONTACT</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
            <p>"Have questions, suggestions, or want to contribute notes? We'd love to hear from you!"</p>
        </div>

        

        <div class="card info-card">
            <h3>Contact Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> notenest@example.com</p>
            <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 24-48 hours</p>
            <p><strong>Best For:</strong> Notes contribution, feedback, technical issues</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card social-card">
            <h3>Connect With Us</h3>
            <p>"Follow us on social media for updates and announcements"</p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">WhatsApp</a>
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#">Email</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>